# `gen_count()`


::: {.cell}

```{.markdown .cell-code}
gen_count(
    text
)
```
:::


- **text**: A string object to be analyzed.

## Examples


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(genCountR)

text <- 'This person was a heroine due to their fighting during the war.'
result_df <- genCountR::gen_count(text)
```
:::
